params.name: with_centering
params.comment: Whether to center the data before scaling.

params.name: with_scaling
params.comment: Whether to scale the data according to the interquartile range.

params.name: copy
params.comment: Whether to make a copy of the input data.

params.name: quantile_range
params.comment: The interquartile range used to scale the data.

params.name: unit_variance
params.comment: Whether to ensure unit variance of the scaled data.
